        "content": "<p>Discover the dynamic streets and rich history of Tbilisi on a comprehensive city tour. Explore the charming Old Town with its narrow cobblestone streets, visit the ancient Narikala Fortress overlooking the city, and admire the magnificent Holy Trinity Cathedral. Walk through the historic districts and experience the vibrant blend of traditional Georgian architecture with modern landmarks that defines this captivating capital city.</p><ul><li>Explore Tbilisi Old Town;</li><li>Visit ancient Narikala Fortress;</li><li>See Holy Trinity Cathedral;</li><li>Walk through historic districts;</li><li>Discover traditional and modern architecture;</li><li>Learn about Tbilisi's rich history;</li><li>Overnight stay in Tbilisi.</li><li><strong>Duration of the tour:</strong> 4-5 hours</li><li><strong>Driving duration:</strong> 30 minutes</li></ul>"
